{"tid":2409183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！公安部：打麻將僅屬娛樂活動 嚴禁賭博！違法人士可被判入獄三年","createTime":"2021-02-15T14:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T04:48:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b180ef2c9c44f2aabf8927a4907c23307e8d62c6","tid":2409183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"公安部強調打麻將只可以是娛樂活動，嚴禁賭博。<br />\n<br />\n公安部指要嚴厲打擊地下流動賭場，特別在城鄉和農村地區調查，深入追蹤組織和經營賭場的人、賭博中的獲利者，以及背後的「保護傘」，壓制賭博違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n公安部指違法人士，輕則被押解到看守所最多十五天和罰款三千元以下人民幣，重則<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>判入獄三年以下。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/602a620d335d19fa24e769cc/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E6%89%93%E9%BA%BB%E5%B0%87%E5%83%85%E5%B1%AC%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%9A%B4%E7%A6%81%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F602a620d335d19fa24e769cc%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%259A%25B4%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E5%258D%259A&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=41734314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/602a620d335d19fa24e769cc/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E6%89%93%E9%BA%BB%E5%B0%87%E5%83%85%E5%B1%AC%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%9A%B4%E7%A6%81%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A</a>"},{"pid":"fa4d717a71b5e13dca49b45202bff5f6cc1155e1","tid":2409183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\